  <brief_title>The Effects of Potassium on Physiological and Cardiovascular Variables in Healthy Persons</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Potassium on Physiological Variables in the Kidney and Cardiovascular Variables in Healthy Persons in a Double-blinded, Randomised, Placebo-controlled, Cross-over Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
