  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In humans living of fruit and vegetables, hypertension is rarely seen. We wish to study if
      the development of hypertension has a connection to our intake of potassium. We know that
      fruit and vegetables contain a lot of potassium and we will simulate this intake by giving
      healthy subjects potassium as tablets.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
